#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Korduma kippuvad küsimused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid "I want to change the way this game looks. Can I?"
msgstr "Ma soovin muuta mängu välimust. On see võimalik?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:247
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes. To change &kolorlines; visual theme you can use "
#| "<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
#| "&kolorlines;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option on the menubar."
msgid ""
"Yes. To change &kolorlines; visual theme you can use the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kolorlines;…"
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Jah. &kolorlines;i teema muutmiseks kasuta menüükäsku "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Seadistused</guimenu><guimenuitem>&kolorlines;i "
"seadistamine...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "I don't want to make any moves right now. Can I skip a turn?"
msgstr "Ma ei taha praegu ühtegi käiku teha. Kas käigu saab vahele jätta?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To skip a turn you can use a <link linkend=\"menu-move-endturn"
"\">keyboard shortcut</link>, or a <link linkend=\"menu-move-endturn"
"\">menubar</link> option."
msgstr ""
"Jah. Käigu vahelejätmiseks kasuta <link linkend=\"menu-move-endturn"
"\">kiirklahvi</link> või vastavat <link linkend=\"menu-move-endturn"
"\">menüükäsku</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play the game?"
msgstr "Kas mängida saab ka klaviatuuri abil?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:255
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Yes. You can use the cursor keys and the <keycap>Space</keycap> key to "
#| "select and set the balls."
msgid ""
"Yes. You can use the cursor keys and the &Space; key to select and set the "
"marbles."
msgstr ""
"Jah. Pallide valimiseks ja paigutamiseks saab kasutada nooleklahve ja "
"<keycap>tühik</keycap>uklahvi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ma ei saa aru, mida ma peaksin tegema! Kas mingeid vihjeid ei ole?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. &kolorlines; does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ei, &kolorlines; ei paku <quote>vihjeid</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Ma pean mängust väljuma, aga mäng ei ole veel läbi. Kas ma saan oma seisu "
"salvestada?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kolorlines; does not have a <quote>Save</quote> feature at the moment."
msgstr "&kolorlines; ei võimalda veel <quote>salvestamist</quote>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Configuration"
msgstr "Mängu seadistamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kolorlines; configuration dialog allows you to select &kolorlines; visual "
"themes."
msgstr ""
"&kolorlines;i seadistustedialoog võimaldab valida &kolorlines;i visuaalse "
"teema"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a new theme simply choose the theme from the selection list. Each "
"item in the list shows a small preview left to the theme name. A selection "
"is immediately applied."
msgstr ""
"Uue teema valimiseks vali see lihtsalt loendist. Kõigi nimekirja elementide "
"juures on teena nimest vasakul näha väike eelvaatlus. Valik rakendatakse "
"kohe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you are satisfied with the theme you have selected you can click the "
"<guibutton>Close</guibutton>, located at the bottom part of this dialog."
msgstr ""
"Kui oled valitud teemaga rahul, klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Sulge</guibutton>, "
"mis asub dialoogi allosas."

